Recommends: spectacle
Description: KDE Plasma 6 panel widget for Claude Code sessions
 KClaude saves Claude Code sessions with name, directory and session ID,
 resumes them with a click in a real terminal, and shows live status plus
 an account-wide rate-limit quota (Claude.ai Pro/Max) in the panel.
